reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality top!
reviews.reviewText: This top is super cute and comfy! Thick material, definitely warm, apricot is a nice neutral color. Runs a little bit big…usually wear a L but the M fits great. Washed on delicate cycle and dried flat….looks good! Will order again in another color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This sweater is comfy and made well. It is thick but not too thick. I think it's perfect for chilly days. It fits true to size for me. I'm normally a large and the large fit me as expected. I'm 5"7 and 163 pounds with a curvy figure and 38dd. The light blue color is really pretty! I will definitely order more colors!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Runs slightly big, great material
reviews.reviewText: I bought this sweater twice. The first 2 pictures show 3 tiny stains on the front of the 1st sweater. The 2nd came & had no stains. The sweater is thicker than I expected but in a good way. The material is very soft and comfortable. I feel like it runs a little big though. I ordered a small & it still had plenty of extra room. I would like an extra small but it's not available in that size. I didn't love the apricot color, it was a bit too yellowish peach. I ended up sending it back. It's a nice sweater but I just wish it was a bit smaller. For reference I'm 5'2 125 lbs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great basic top
reviews.reviewText: I am often cautious of clothing from Amazon that isn’t a brand I would find in the store. This item was a great buy though. Thick material, true to size, comfortable, and has washed well. I air dry rather than using the dryer and wash inside out with cold water. The tag wasn’t clear on fabric care.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Nice quality sweater! Medium weight, nice pattern. Love the split sides and color. I weigh 170 and got the medium. Fits perfect. Still a little roomy but nice fitting.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute and soft but..
reviews.reviewText: It was cute and soft but it’s very boxy. Has no shape when you’re wearing it. Runs big. Returned it. I wanted something less squared boxy shape. Has no curves to the shape of the sweater. Sleeves near the wrists are kinda tight as well and I have tiny child like wrists lol

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BUY THIS TOP
reviews.reviewText: I cannot recommend this top enough! I sent it to all my female relatives and friends 🤣 it is the perfect relaxed, yet tailored fit. The material is thick and comfortable. It feels much higher end than the price reflects. Definitely a new staple in my wardrobe. Can’t wait to purchase it in more colors!PS - sizing does tend to run a bit big. I normally wear a medium in tops from Loft/J. Crew/similar brands but wear a small in this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality, feels great
reviews.reviewText: I ordered medium and am 5'8 and it fits very well. Fabric is strong, but comfy and drapes nicely. I have another color coming.. this has a drop shoulder seam, but it's still flattering. The stripes aren't overpowering, so doesn't draw attention to hips or waist. Nice product
